  "texts": [
    "As our comprehension of the asymptotic case has advanced, there is a pressing need for tools with improved constants.",
    "The main objective of DP is to safeguard private data from being leaked to an adversary.",
    "DP accomplishes this goal by providing a provable guarantee, which is a generic bound on privacy leakage that makes few assumptions about the goals and capabilities of an adversary.",
    "However, DP has some limitations that need to be considered.",
    "Firstly, the DP bound may not provide stakeholders with sufficient information about the degree to which the system is initially vulnerable to specific attacks against the privacy of data."
  ],
